cutscene_segment_set(0, "Welcome to the United States of Craziness, where everything is chill and dope. This galaxy is the happy home of the Freaks, a fun loving people who do whatever harmless thing they want.", spr_cutscene_intro_1,,, msc_cutscene_intro);
cutscene_segment_set(1, "This is all thanks to Unlimit Energy, a mystical energy that permeates the entire universe. When gathered in large enough quantities, Unlimit Energy allows a person to rewrite reality.", spr_cutscene_intro_2,,,,, cutscene_transitions.fade);
cutscene_segment_set(2, "The more of it one has, the stronger they become. Naturally, while Unlimit Energy has solved every crisis that has ever faced our galaxy, evil-doers still exist and try to steal Unlimit Energy for their own evil purposes.");
cutscene_segment_set(3, "Unlimit Energy has also given rise to real superheroes. The Super Freaks, and their beloved relative Uncle Swordsman, wield Unlimit Energy in battle to combat the various supervillains that threaten the USC.", spr_cutscene_intro_3,,,,, cutscene_transitions.fade);
cutscene_segment_set(4, "They are known for their versatility and ability to use any power ever, especially the stupid ones. But one fateful day, the Super Freaks' arch enemy Mikey 'Kranion' Ribson Jr. invited himself over to play some games...");

cutscene_segment_set(5, "Kranion: 'What the freak!!!! This game is wicked stupid!'", spr_cutscene_intro_4,,, msc_cutscene_normal);
cutscene_segment_set(6, "Scruffy: 'Dude, we keep telling you, you gotta drift around the corners!'", spr_cutscene_intro_5,,,,, cutscene_transitions.NA);
cutscene_segment_set(7, "Kranion: 'You guys ah a couple ijits, I bagged you cheatahs bangin' a u-ie at wicked impossible speeds!'");
cutscene_segment_set(8, "King Quincy: 'Yeah, you don't keep tapping the gas, you have to hold it. We can show you how to do it again!'");
cutscene_segment_set(9, "Kranion: 'Nah, screw you guys! I'm goin' to hang with my real friends in Wistah. See ya later, bozos.'", spr_cutscene_intro_6,,,,, cutscene_transitions.NA);
cutscene_segment_set(10, "Gambi: 'What an idiot.'");
cutscene_segment_set(11, "Tikiman: 'Aw, give him a minute and he'll cool off. Mikey's just upset that he can't beat us in Fast Cars Underground 2. He'll be as good as us someday!'");
cutscene_segment_set(12, "Oh Tikiman, you sweet, innocent, thing. Kranion would be more than good as you. He would be better--much better. Much better than us all.'");

cutscene_segment_set(13, "Kranion, backed by his army of killer Kranibots, and his pure, unadultered saltiness, staged a massive invasion of the entire galaxy, starting with the Super Freaks' super cool stadium.", spr_cutscene_intro_7,,, msc_boss_1,, cutscene_transitions.fade);
cutscene_segment_set(14, "Gambi: 'Dude, what the actual hell?'");
cutscene_segment_set(15, "Kranion: 'You asked for it, chumps. Nevah mess with a proud chowdahead! Me and my boys are gonna steal all that Unlimit crap yah guys use tah cheat at life, and I'm gonna use it tah be thuh best Fast Cahs Undahground 2 playah that evah lived!'", spr_cutscene_intro_8,,,,, cutscene_transitions.NA);
cutscene_segment_set(16, "Scruffy: 'You did all this because we clowned on you in a game from 2004?'", spr_cutscene_intro_9,,,,, cutscene_transitions.fade);
cutscene_segment_set(17, "The Super Freaks laughed at the sheer pettiness of their arch-enemy.");
cutscene_segment_set(18, "Kranion: 'Yeah, maybe I did! Someone had ta put yah dweebs in ya place. You beat up me, my dad, and a buncha othah guys thanks to this magic crap, so let's see yah try ta beat me without it! Latah, losers!!!'", spr_cutscene_intro_10,,,,, cutscene_transitions.fade);
cutscene_segment_set(19, "Gambi: 'Great. Now what do we do? We have no superpowers!'", spr_cutscene_intro_11,,,,, cutscene_transitions.fade);
cutscene_segment_set(20, "Tikiman: 'Michael underestimates one thing about us. We can fight even without any powers!'");
cutscene_segment_set(21, "King Quincy: 'Tikiman's right. Mikey may be a super powerful reality warper who's probably going to kill us, but that's not going to stop us!'");
cutscene_segment_set(22, "Scruffy: 'That's right! We might only be able to move and jump right now, but we're good at it!'");
cutscene_segment_set(23, "And so, the Super Freaks set out to defeat Kranion and take back the galaxy's supply of Unlimit Energy. Will they succeed without their source of superpowers?");
cutscene_segment_set(24, "Well, yeah, obviously. But they're gonna need the help of one to four random people with gamepads. That's you!");